data.description: Nestled on Evansville's Eastside, this charming 2 to 3 bedroom, 1 bath full-brick home sits gracefully on a corner lot, offering comfort and style. With 948 square feet of living space, this residence boasts a spacious 1.5 car attached garage, providing both convenience and functionality. Step inside to discover a welcoming atmosphere complemented by recent updates. The home features a multitude of improvements, including a new roof installed just 3.5 years ago. The recently remodeled bathroom showcases all-new ceramic tile, lending a modern and elegant touch to the space. The interior exudes fresh appeal with newer carpeting and paint throughout, creating a cozy and inviting ambiance in every room. The beautifully updated kitchen is adorned with stainless steel appliances, offering both style and functionality for culinary enthusiasts. Outside, the yard has been thoughtfully fenced in with a wood privacy fence, providing security and seclusion while creating an ideal space for outdoor enjoyment and relaxation. This home perfectly marries modern updates with classic charm, presenting an opportunity for comfortable living in a move-in-ready residence in a desirable location on Evansville's Eastside.
